Template: composer/UPDATE_APPS
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Update applications with new composer
 Find all /usr/share/*/composer.json + /usr/lib/*/composer.json and perform updates ?

Template: composer/WEB_USER
Type: string
Default: www-data
Description: Chown system-wide composer files
 Chown all in  /var/lib/composer/  to given user ?
